data.description: Nestled on Woodberry Ln, this charming home offers 2BRs plus a bonus room perfect for play or work. Situated on 2 acres (with almost an acre fenced in), enjoy serene surroundings, 2 sheds for storage, and 2 fire pits for outdoor gatherings. Thoughtfully designed for comfort and convenience, with the seller's personal touch evident throughout. Ideal for entertainers, downsizers, or first-time buyers seeking comfort and versatility.
